<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">AI search is changing how customers find your business. Traditional SEO isn't enough anymore. You need specialised strategies to appear in ChatGPT, Google's AI Overviews, and other AI-powered search tools.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Our AI search visibility services ensure your brand shows up when AI systems answer customer questions. We optimise your content for AI crawlers and improve your chances of being featured in AI responses.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Do</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We analyse how AI systems currently see your business. Our team identifies gaps in your AI search presence and creates a custom strategy to improve visibility.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Our services include content optimisation for AI crawlers. We restructure your existing content to match how AI systems process information. This includes adding structured data and improving content clarity.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We also create AI-friendly content that answers common customer questions. This content is designed to be easily understood and cited by AI systems. We focus on the questions your customers actually ask.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Technical optimisation is another key service. We ensure your website structure supports AI crawling. This includes improving page speed, mobile responsiveness, and structured markup.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We provide ongoing monitoring of your AI search performance. Our reports show which AI platforms are citing your content and how often you appear in AI responses.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">How We Work</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We start with a comprehensive AI search audit. This reveals your current visibility across major AI platforms. We identify your biggest opportunities for improvement.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Next, we develop your AI search strategy. This includes keyword research specifically for AI queries. We also map out content gaps that need addressing.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Implementation follows a proven process. We optimise existing content first, then create new AI-friendly content. Technical improvements run alongside content work.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We track results through specialist AI monitoring tools. These show your performance across different AI platforms. You receive monthly reports with clear insights and recommendations.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Our Pricing</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Our starter package costs £1,500 per month. This includes basic AI search optimisation for up to 20 pages. You get monthly performance reports and ongoing content recommendations.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">The professional package is £3,500 monthly. This covers comprehensive optimisation for up to 50 pages. It includes new content creation and technical optimisation. You also get priority support and detailed analytics.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Enterprise clients pay £6,000+ per month. This includes unlimited page optimisation and custom AI strategies. We provide dedicated account management and advanced reporting. Pricing depends on your specific requirements.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">All packages include a detailed audit and strategy document. Setup fees may apply for complex technical implementations. We offer flexible contract terms to suit different business needs.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Ready to Improve Your AI Search Visibility?</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Don't let competitors dominate AI search results. Start improving your visibility today with our proven AI search optimisation services.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Get a free AI search audit worth £500. We'll analyse your current visibility and show you exactly where you're missing opportunities. No obligation required.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Contact us now to claim your free audit and discuss your AI search strategy. Our experts are ready to help you succeed in the age of AI search.</p>
